    "summary": "Real transformation is about people, not technology. This might sound like a no-brainer, but involvement and support of people remain one of the key challenges of IT business transformation. Too often organisations tend to invest time and resources in state of art technical architecture, software selection, project methodology and process optimization alone \u2013 but forget to involve the people that make or break the adoption of the transition.\n\nAs seasoned (+15 years) IT business transformation professional Boy ensures people and organisational change are embedded in the project. Combined with a granular and structured approach Boy directs the project to both realizing (technical) milestones in time, as building the required support for change. \n\nWith a solid background in business operations, finance and regulatory reporting, he adapts easily to any business or industry. Boy is driven by results, motivated by building winning teams and is getting things done.\n\n\nSpecialties\nLeading business software implementations, ERP (Dynamics 365, SAP S4/HANA, FiCo, Salesforce C360), People manager & leader, IT Program & Project Management, Digital transformation, Agile & Scrum, Winning team builder, Change management, Process optimisation & automation, Data migration, KYC & Regulatory reporting, Finance & accounting, Business operational excellence.",
